      <title>日元疲软推动日本股市上涨；银行股收益率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/japanese-stocks-set-to-jump-after-us-jobs-data-spur-yen-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于就业报告强于预期，凸显了美国经济的韧性，日元下跌，日本股市上涨。随着日本基准债券收益率上升，东京金融股上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/japanese-stocks-set-to-jump-after-us-jobs-data-spur-yen-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:39:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
