    <item>
      <title>交易员关注以色列对伊朗袭击的回应，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-7</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周油价开盘走低，市场等待观察以色列是否会对上周的导弹袭击对伊朗进行报复，美国总统乔·拜登也不鼓励对伊朗油田进行袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-7</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:31:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>富时指数调整 韩国、印度债券市场备受关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/ftse-s-index-revamp-has-korean-indian-bond-markets-on-watch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国已尽一切努力将其债券纳入主要的富时罗素指数，而印度则避开了公共改革 — — 但后者在全球投资者中的受欢迎程度可能使其在加入相关基准指数方面具有优势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-06/ftse-s-index-revamp-has-korean-indian-bond-markets-on-watch</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 06 Oct 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
